$lang['When it comes to binary coding, Hexadecimal is more efficient because it reduces 8 digits to 2. Additionally, Hex provides a greater degree of information density and higher accuracy in numbers than binary does. This is due to the fact that Hex uses 16 symbols instead of just two like binary. Because of this increased efficiency, Hexadecimal is often used when binary coding in computing and digital electronics as well as for computer science applications.'] = 'Raha mikasika ny kaody binary, ny Hexadecimal dia mahomby kokoa satria mampihena ny isa 8 ho 2. Fanampin&#39;izany, ny Hex dia manome mari-pahaizana ambony kokoa amin&#39;ny fampahalalam-baovao sy marina kokoa amin&#39;ny isa noho ny binary. Izany dia noho ny zava-misy fa ny Hex dia mampiasa marika 16 fa tsy roa fotsiny toy ny binary. Noho ny fahombiazan&#39;io fitomboana io dia matetika ny Hexadecimal no ampiasaina rehefa kaody binary amin&#39;ny informatika sy elektronika nomerika ary koa ho an&#39;ny fampiharana siansa informatika.';
$lang['In addition, Hexadecimal takes up less space than decimal. With only two digits instead of 8 binary digits, Hex numbers represent large numbers much more concisely. This can be very helpful when working with computer systems, as there is less chance for mistakes when typing in hex codes compared to decimal codes which have so many decimal points all over the place!'] = 'Ankoatra izany, ny Hexadecimal dia maka toerana kely kokoa noho ny decimal. Miaraka amin&#39;ny isa roa fotsiny fa tsy tarehimarika mimari-droa 8, ny isa Hex dia maneho isa lehibe kokoa. Mety hanampy tokoa izany rehefa miasa amin&#39;ny rafitra informatika, satria kely kokoa ny mety hisian&#39;ny hadisoana rehefa manoratra kaody hex raha oharina amin&#39;ny kaody desimal izay manana teboka desimal be dia be manerana ny toerana!';
