$lang['Similarly, after reaching 9 in Hexadecimal (represented by “F”), we start counting again at 10 (“10”). This pattern continues until we reach 15 (“1F”), at which point we reset back to 0 and begin counting again at 16 (“20”). This might sound confusing at first, but with a little practice, it will become second nature!'] = 'Toy izany koa, rehefa mahatratra 9 amin&#39;ny Hexadecimal (misolo tena ny &quot;F&quot;), dia manomboka manisa indray isika amin&#39;ny 10 (&quot;10&quot;). Ity lamina ity dia mitohy mandra-pahatongantsika amin&#39;ny 15 (&quot;1F&quot;), amin&#39;izay fotoana izay dia avereno amin&#39;ny 0 ary manomboka manisa indray amin&#39;ny 16 (&quot;20&quot;). Mety ho mampisavoritaka izany amin&#39;ny voalohany, saingy amin&#39;ny fampiharana kely dia ho lasa toetra faharoa izany!';
